Lumi core project marker

This file marks the repository as the canonical Lumi application project.

Agent features and development-only UI (such as \"Add Dev Context to Chat\") can use
the presence of this file to detect that they are running inside Lumi itself,
instead of a user project that merely embeds Lumi components.

Do not reference machine-specific paths or secrets here. The file is intentionally
simple and text-only so that it is safe to commit and easy to check for in tools.

